features: Cable Holder for Car: Our cord organizer are super useful for organizing cables. It will prevent your Phone charging cables, USB cables, network cables, TV power cords from excessive bending tangling and fray, keep your room tidy and neat.

Adhesive Cable Clips: This phone cord holder for desk comes with a strong 3M adhesive pad that can adhere to any smooth and clean surfaces at home or office, such as glass, plastic, metal or wood tables, desks and walls. Easy to install no need to hammer holes or attach screws.
Silicone Cable Organizer: These wire management are made of high quality eco-friendly and flexible silicone material that bends easily and insert the cables smoothly.

Suitable for Daily Use: Our cord clips suitable for the wire diameter within 0.26 inch(6mm). You can not only use it as a wire clip, but also as a pen holder, a toothbrush, or floss holders. Perfect size to meet your daily use requirements.

Little Tips: For better use of our wire organizers, please make sure the desk surface is clean smooth, oil-free, dust-free, and water-free before stick it. And keep it for at least several hours after fixation, 24 hours is better.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Okay, you have to buy these! I have bought so many of these from five below, shein & then I got these & THEY ARE AMAZING! I love that they come in two different sizes and they stick so well, I put one on my wall. Maybe that was a bad idea. Haven’t taken it off yet so I’m not sure yet. They hold the cords extremely well, the other day I tripped over one and it still was in place soooo yes great grip & hold. This was exactly what I needed to keep my cords organized.The adhesion is great it’s durable and easy to use and stick on, I stuck it on a metal cart, and one I stuck on my wall, and they work great!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The purpose is great, adhesion is not
reviews.reviewText: I love the purpose that this item fulfills, and that you can put multiple cords on it. But they just do not stick for very long. The adhesion is the only problem for me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Neutral color/size and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: I have two lap tops plus chargers and wires that were a complete mess, this picture shows on cord but the ability to add 4 more. It's easy to lightly pull the cords to bring them closer without having to unhook or have free hanging cords. This stuck very easily to my table top and I was able to easily re-position then re-adhere to my desk when I didn't initially like the placement.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Tidy little gadget. Great design and extremely useful. Makes a great gift, too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I’ve tried other brands and other adhesives and they all are crap compared to this one. This thing is awesome! Works as advertised and the adhesive is very strong! Definitely recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The adhesive on the back is very strong and it won’t budge when you’re moving cords in and out of it. This saves time digging through multiple cords plugged into the same outlet trying to find the end of it. I purchased 2 and use them for my phone and watch chargers and also have one stuck to the side of my desk organizing my laptop, iPad, and Apple Pencil chargers. I’m surprised the product is so affordable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I have a million cables that I don't want to bend over to pick up and plug in. With this I just pull and plug. I still have one that I could use, which I will keep around for around the house. I will say I have found these for way cheaper (like 1.99 cheap) but I can't speak to their quality. This one is nice and gummy and it does not budge when glued on. I Also like that you can choose different colors.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars These are for cables not plug wire
reviews.reviewText: Works ok. Adhesive ok...but not strong. Fell off already as I was hanging it from the side of desk not top. These are only for small cable wires. Will not hold a plug wire.
